ZH: 消费者在购买商品时应该注意品质。
EN: Consumers should pay attention to the quality when purchasing products.

ZH: 消费者有权利知道商品的具体信息。
EN: Consumers have the right to know the specific information of the products.

ZH: 消费者对于售后服务应该有保障。
EN: Consumers should have protection for after-sales services.

ZH: 消费者对于价格的变动应该有适当的通知。
EN: Consumers should be appropriately notified of price changes.

ZH: 消费者在购物时应该谨慎比较价格。
EN: Consumers should compare prices carefully when shopping.

ZH: 消费者应该被尊重和保护。
EN: Consumers should be respected and protected.

ZH: 消费者对于欺诈行为应该保持警惕。
EN: Consumers should be vigilant against fraudulent behavior.

ZH: 消费者在选择产品时应该慎重考虑。
EN: Consumers should carefully consider when choosing products.

ZH: 消费者在市场中应该具有消费者意识。
EN: Consumers should have consumer awareness in the market.

ZH: 消费者在购买时应该慎重选择商家。
EN: Consumers should carefully choose merchants when making purchases.

ZH: 消费者对于虚假广告应该有投诉权。
EN: Consumers should have the right to complain about false advertising.

ZH: 消费者在购买时应该主动保护自己的权益。
EN: Consumers should actively protect their own rights and interests when making purchases.

ZH: 消费者在维权时应该寻求专业帮助。
EN: Consumers should seek professional help when protecting their rights.

ZH: 消费者对于服务质量有权提出意见。
EN: Consumers have the right to voice opinions on service quality.

ZH: 消费者在购物过程中应该遵守规则。
EN: Consumers should follow the rules during the shopping process.

ZH: 消费者应该有权知悉产品的成分和质量标准。
EN: Consumers should have the right to know the ingredients and quality standards of products.

ZH: 消费者在选择商品时应该看重性价比。
EN: Consumers should value the cost-effectiveness when choosing products.

ZH: 消费者在购买时应该避免盲目跟风。
EN: Consumers should avoid blindly following trends when making purchases.

ZH: 消费者在购买之前应该仔细阅读产品说明书。
EN: Consumers should read the product instructions carefully before making a purchase.
